<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #FFFBF5; color: #1A1208; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-w: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8441A, #F59E0B); border-radius: 12px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1A1208; text-align: center; }
    p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4A3728; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .order-box { background: white; border: 2px solid #F0E6D8; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .order-header { font-weight: 800; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0E6D8; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #B5957D; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">🍕</div>
    </div>
    <h1>We've received your order!</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Great choice! Your order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> has been placed and is currently pending confirmation. We will notify you once it's confirmed and being prepared.</p>
    
    <div class="order-box">
      <div class="order-header">
        <span>Order #{{orderId}}</span>
        <span>₹{{totalAmount}}</span>
      </div>
      <p style="margin:0; font-size: 14px;">Track your order status in your profile on the website.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      © {{year}} Slice of Swadesh. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
